{"/service/ndnp/ndhi/batch_ndhi_jud_ver01/data/sn88076421/00212476079/1921033101/0186.xml":{"full_text":"A\nBIG\nMAN\n\"V\nMINOT Second to None MINOT\nDon't Stop Minot Now-Keep Her Going Forward\nW. S. SHAW\nSMC\nPresident Shaw^has given us his untiring energy to make Minot a Real City, a Better\nCity, the Best of its size in the world.\nSHAW HAS MADE GOOD\nAfter four years of crop failures, two years of war, with its high co& of living and\nnationwide business depression caused by the recon&rudtion,\nMinot is Bigger and Better Today Than Ever Before\nKEEP MINOT ON THE MAP!\nShaw's administration got us the viadudt, our well system and reservoir, our Paving.\nHe supported our parks and schools. Minot Is All Right.\n13\nfell::\nFOR\nA BIG\nJOB\n(Political Advertising)","height":"24936","width":"17650"}}
